arStrings.szText: "Weren't you human? How did you become a spirit?"
I was once a part of Akarat, I think. He was indeed human, and so very loved. So much that when he lay dying, none of his Dedicants would let him go as he wished.
One of them, the first of the Spiritborn, found a way to chase his soul to the Spirit Realm. I do not know what she did there. Only that it hurt, when I was born.
